import React from 'react'; const About = () => { return (

About Me

I want to build something great

Five years ago, I started a coding bootcamp with a $25 ad on craigslist. I was able to help hundreds of students change their lives forever while growing Codify Academy to a million dollar company in just 3 years. I loved building out the course, coding in house apps, and helping students understand the complex nuances of front-end web development. With Codify winding down, I'm looking to get back into coding full time. If you're company makes cool things and needs a good web developer, let's schedule a call.

); } export default About;
